sequenceDiagram
    participant Actor
    participant API as Governance API
    participant GSM as Governance State Machine
    participant DB as Decision Store
    participant XSM as Execution State Machine

    Actor->>API: Envelope(PROPOSE)
    API->>GSM: validate + transition(DRAFT → PROPOSED)
    GSM->>DB: persist decision + history

    Actor->>API: Envelope(CHALLENGE)
    API->>GSM: transition(PROPOSED → UNDER_DELIBERATION)
    GSM->>DB: store challenge

    Actor->>API: Envelope(TEST)
    API->>GSM: transition(→ UNDER_TEST)
    GSM->>DB: store test results

    Actor->>API: Envelope(ADJUDICATE)
    API->>GSM: validate challenges resolved
    GSM->>DB: set ADJUDICATED

    Actor->>API: Envelope(LEGITIMIZE)
    API->>GSM: validate authority
    GSM->>DB: set LEGITIMIZED

    Actor->>API: Envelope(EXECUTE)
    API->>XSM: dispatch execution
    XSM->>DB: update execution state

    XSM->>API: execution result
    API->>DB: record outcome

    Actor->>API: Envelope(RECORD)
    API->>DB: persist record

    Actor->>API: Envelope(LEARN)
    API->>DB: store lessons
